  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates that YY1 acts as a key transcription factor in H. pylori-induced gastric carcinogenesis by directly activating JAK2 transcription and promoting JAK2/STAT3-mediated epithelial-mesenchymal transition.",
    "The research provides evidence for YY1 as both a biomarker and potential therapeutic target in gastric cancer, particularly in H. pylori-associated cases."
